{"tid":2094823,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"英國政府用 6 年做標準其實好醒","createTime":"2020-07-05T03:51:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-05T15:15:22.000Z","uid":332538,"like":60,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"ba66786f2e792988cb1f4a759e0681b2f3c584c5","tid":2094823,"uid":332538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T03:51:12.000Z","msg":"1. 留 6 年 有 BC<br />\n2. 6 年唔俾福利<br />\n3. 每年出境有限制日數<br />\n4. 有權讀書同搵野做，讀書計外人價<br />\n<br />\n基本上有呢幾個條件<br />\n唔洗有資產條件<br />\n已經清走一大堆廢青廢老<br />\n同埋睇你嘅決心同忠誠程度<br />\n仲有，英國有 5 年時間審查你/你家人在港期間有無做過損害自由嘅事<br />\n有哂證據就唔俾你入藉<br />\n<br />\n所以就算三百萬人有<br />\n可能真係過去嘅都係得幾十萬<br />\n主要以家庭為主"},{"pid":"7399ae70a02ffbbbf155134a16de3f4b92c62ef1","tid":2094823,"uid":134683,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T03:53:16.000Z","msg":"唔係話18歲以下可以讀state school咩？"},{"pid":"de973256ff2894bab758d3e8d2e6af5a648f49d0","tid":2094823,"uid":81309,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":8,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T03:55:36.000Z","msg":"乜原來讀書計外人價？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb264cefdb2333c6f0950e9e7cda96b526af8286","tid":2094823,"uid":189109,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"de973256ff2894bab758d3e8d2e6af5a648f49d0","tid":2094823,"uid":81309,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":8,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T03:55:36.000Z","msg":"乜原來讀書計外人價？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T03:59:03.000Z","msg":"你又唔係BC 梗係計international<br />\n不過唔趕住讀可以做住嘢先 拎咗BC先讀"},{"pid":"441683aa19d6e78db949606e1cb6ef909ebcb03c","tid":2094823,"uid":127929,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"quote":{"pid":"de973256ff2894bab758d3e8d2e6af5a648f49d0","tid":2094823,"uid":81309,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":8,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T03:55:36.000Z","msg":"乜原來讀書計外人價？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T04:04:19.000Z","msg":"將心比己姐, 宜家啲蝗蟲係香港讀書要納稅人埋